      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>John joined Defra in March 2016 following a 25 year career in the private sector.</p>

<p>Previously he was Group CIO at Abellio, a leader in the provision of public transport services in Europe, and Global IT Director at Ipsos, a market research leader with offices in 85 countries. John is at ease operating internationally, backed by a multi-cultural profile having worked and lived in the UK, France, Greece, Lebanon, Germany, Luxembourg, and Spain.</p>

<p>He is native in Greek and English, and fluent in French and Spanish.</p>
</div>
      </section>

